scms
=====
scms is a simple static content management system for web and gopher.
It uses mk as build system, goblin for some commands, md2htm to convert Markdown files to HTML
and pp to preprocess them. Also it's possible to run mk after changing files inside of net
or inc directory with entr to make compiling of files automatic.

Usage
-----
	% mk # To compile static files.

	% mk run # To start automatic polling files change.

